reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These chargers are a perfect match for the Samsung Galaxy s21 Ultra phones
reviews.reviewText: I usually purchase nothing but Samsung original chargers for my phones. When I purchased two Samsung Galaxy s21 Ultras, I decided to check several different Brand chargers to see how they would compare in quality and operation. For my wife's Galaxy s21 Ultra, ONLY the best. I selected an Anker brand charger, which was the best quality, appearance, and heaviest; (heavy is usually a good thing in power supplies). For my Galaxy s21 Ultra, I tried several less expensive chargers, but with good specifications. I have been testing these from The Duloch Store. I have been very satisfied with their performance. They look presentable, operate cool, FAST charge, everything I wanted, and I received two chargers for the price I paid for some of the other brands I purchased. At some point, I will cut one open to check the design, (because that is what I do with all of them), but for now, I find them an outstanding value and with outstanding performance. Good Stuff!
